``` curt
define rectangle @ bbox: { t: [0, 0], w: bbox.width, h: bbox.height }
def area r = r.w * r.h
def perimeter r = 2 * (r.w + r.h)
def scale r factor = rectangle { t: r.t, w: r.w * factor, h: r.h * factor }

"fmt %f %f\n" (area (rectangle { w: 3.0, h: 4.0 }))
"fmt %f %f\n" (perimeter (rectangle { w: 3.0, h: 4.0 }))
"fmt %f %f\n" (area (scale (rectangle { w: 3.0, h: 4.0 }) 2.0))
```<|im_end|>
